list.abstract: sector 是c语言函数名。功能是画并填充椭圆扇区。

yingyinNormal.en: And that's the longest streak of private-sector job growth on record.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是有史以来持续最长时间私营部门的就业增长。

yingyinNormal.en: That's the longest uninterrupted stretch of private sector job creation in our history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我们历史上私营部门持续最长时间的就业机会增长。

yingyinNormal.en: That's the longest uninterrupted stretch of private sector job creation in our history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我们历史上持续最长时间私营部门不间断地创造着就业岗位。

yingyinNormal.en: Infrastructure at the state and federal level. Increasing the size of the military, and working with our friends in the private sector to start…
yingyinNormal.zh: 州和联邦基础建设项目，扩大军队，并与私营部门合作。

yingyinNormal.en: That's the longest streak of private-sector job creation in our history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是历史上私营企业所取得的最好的成绩。

yingyinNormal.en: We were in the dark on this also. It was director only clearance at Sector 7, until now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这事儿我们也不知道，今天以前只有主管能进入第7区。

yingyinNormal.en: It doesn't matter. As long as we steer clear of whichever sector is active, we'll be safe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无所谓了，避开活跃中的区域我们就安全。

yingyinNormal.en: We know that she is in sector five. This is a game we call hide-and-seek. It's a scent drill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们知道她现在在第五区，这场游戏我们称之为躲猫猫，是气味演习。

yingyinNormal.en: Two weeks ago, Wilkins left a lucrative job in the tech sector to found a new charity called O.T.P.S.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两周前，威尔金斯辞去了收入颇丰的技术职务，创建了一个慈善组织，名叫OTPS。

yingyinNormal.en: Good God, the government couldn't afford this kind of facility. No, it was benefactors mostly, from the private sector.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，政府哪有钱盖这种大楼，大部分还得靠私营企业捐助。

yingyinNormal.en: You used the tunnels to infiltrate yourself into the White House, somehow conning your way into the blue sector, all to try and warn her?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你之前从隧道侵入白宫，还想办法进入到了蓝区，你做这些都是为了警告她吗

yingyinNormal.en: And even if I could have predicted I would one day work in the private sector, I never could have predicted Facebook, because there was no internet, and Mark Zuckerberg was at elementary school, already wearing his hoody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就算我算到了自己会在私营企业工作，我肯定也算不到自己会在Facebook。因为当时没有互联网，马克·扎克伯格还在读小学，已经开始穿他的标志性帽衫了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The gender pay gap based on median salaries across the <highlight>sector</highlight> in 2016 -2017 was 13.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 基于 2016 年至 2017 年整个行业的薪水中位数，性别薪酬差距为 13。

examination_example.sentence: Now, the number of men working in the nursing <highlight>sector</highlight> has reached a seven-year low.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在，在护理部门工作的男性人数达到了7年来的最低水平。

examination_example.sentence: These stages will span <highlight>sectors</highlight>, take people to different cities, and provide foundation for building a wide variety of skills.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些阶段将涵盖多个领域，把人们带到不同的城市，为培养各种各样的技能打下基础。
